data.title: Ionic Lithium Deep Cycle Batteries & Products
data.meta_description: LithiumHub are the creators of the Ionic lithium deep cycle batteries & other lithium battery products; marine, RV, solar, scooter, chargers & much more!
data.text:
LithiumHub, home of the IONIC Lithium Battery, is proud to announce the first ever IONIC Lithium Battery Champions Invitational Bass Tournament. This 2-day tournament will be like no other with a $100k total cash prize.

We will be inviting the top 5 finishers in each division, including Bassmaster Elite, Bassmaster Open, MFL BassPro Tour, MFL Invitationals, MFL Toyota, NPFL, and Collegiate.
